  "summary": "Within sections: body letter-spacing 0; ALL-CAPS callouts/CTAs +0.5px; no negative tracking in email; paragraph spacing: headline-subhead 8px, subhead-body 12px, headline-body 12px, body paragraphs 12px, body-CTA 16px."
